      "blocks": {
        "text_kyQwPd": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text_content_header": "Financing",
            "text_content": "<p>If you are working with a limited budget and want to spread project costs out over time, financing is the perfect solution! With financing, your playground continues to grow as you install segments of equipment incrementally, paying for each addition as it’s built. You can have the playground of your dreams completed in as little as 3-5 phases.<\/p><p><br\/>Benefits Of Financing include:<\/p><ul><li>Flexibility that allows you to pay as you go<\/li><li>Affordable options that don't stretch your budget too thin<\/li><li>New features are added to your playground each year<\/li><\/ul>",
            "text-alignment": "center",
            "background": "#ffffff"
          }
        }
      },
