            "caption": "Financing & Leasing",
            "heading": "Leasing",
            "text": "<p>Do you want to design, build and install your complete plaground as quickly as possible? Our leasing partner, Marlin, offers an easy and affordable way to fund your new play area NOW and pay for it over time. With Marlin, you can get the playground you need, with a plan that fits your budget!<\/p><p>Our leasing plan provides you with the flexibility, and funds needed to get your project started now, with attractive rates, potential tax advantages, and a simple step-by-step application process.<\/p>",
